data.description: First time on the market...Welcome to this BEAUTIFUL 4 bedroom, 2 1/2 Bath Colonial home nestled in the heart of Carbon County. This home is surrounded by breathtaking serene mountain views perfect for you to enjoy your morning coffee.  This property sits just 2 minutes from Beltzville Lake and State Park, where you can enjoy many outdoor activities like picnicking, fishing, swimming, boating, hiking, Jet skiing, and kayaking;  AND is only 20 minutes from Blue Mountain Ski Resort where you can enjoy, skiing, snowboarding, and snow tubing in the winter months!  Easy to show and won't last long!!!
